OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779027072
OL,3,CSpiritual leaders gather for
OL,4,Cinterfaith peace conference
OL,6,FThe 19th National Peace Symposium has
OL,7,Ftaken place in Surrey, to address the
OL,8,Furgent need for world-wide justice and
OL,9,Flasting peace.
OL,11,FMore than 600 faith leaders,
OL,12,Fpoliticians and charities attended the
OL,13,Fconference at the Mubarak Mosque in
OL,14,FTilford, the global headquarters of
OL,15,Fthe Ahmadiyya Muslim Community.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
