PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779027072
OL,3,CSpiritual leaders gather for
OL,4,Cinterfaith peace conference
OL,6,FThe event, now in its 19th year, was
OL,7,Fdesigned to explore pressing global
OL,8,Fchallenges and the urgent need for
OL,9,Fjustice as a pathway to lasting peace,
OL,10,Fwith discussions touching on current
OL,11,Fconflicts in Iran, Palestine, Ukraine
OL,12,Fand beyond.
OL,14,FThe keynote address was delivered by
OL,15,FHis Holiness, Hazrat Mirza Masroor
OL,16,FAhmad, the worldwide head of the
OL,17,FAhmadiyya Muslim Community.
OL,19,FWATCH: Delegates Sabah Ahmedi and
OL,20,FAdeel Shah speak about the importance
OL,21,Fof the symposium.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
