PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779027072
OL,3,CSpiritual leaders gather for
OL,4,Cinterfaith peace conference
OL,6,FHe advocated for justice, dialogue and
OL,7,Fsustainable peace, and warned of
OL,8,Fescalating tensions, including the
OL,9,Fthreat of nuclear conflict and a
OL,10,Fpotential world war.
OL,12,FHe told the delegates that political
OL,13,Fleaders need to put aside selfish
OL,14,Fdesires and vested interests and focus
OL,15,Finstead on building connections
OL,16,Fbetween disparate groups.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
