PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779027072
OL,3,CSpiritual leaders gather for
OL,4,Cinterfaith peace conference
OL,6,FThe symposium addressed the rise of
OL,7,Fnationalism in many countries, and
OL,8,Finjustice fuelling conflict, poverty
OL,9,Fand inequality, creating humanitarian
OL,10,Fcrises across the globe.
OL,12,FSpeakers called for unity for the
OL,13,Fcause of peace and spoke of the
OL,14,Fimportance of continued dialogue.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
